title: Samsung Galaxy Tab S2 9.7-inch Unboxing and First Impressions
description:
Hands-on with the 9.7-inch Samsung Galaxy Tab S2. Some of its specs include an Exynos 5433 octa-core processor, 3GB of RAM, 8MP camera sensor, 9.7-inch Super AMOLED display, and TouchWiz running on Android 5.0 Lollipop. Starting at $499, do you think the 9.7-inch Galaxy Tab S2 is worth your money?

Check out Beau HD's personal channel: http://goo.gl/E5iM4N

8.0" Galaxy Tab S2 Unboxing & First Impressions: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kNDYH439GC0
